com.gensym.util
Class DefinitionEvent

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--java.util.EventObject
        |
        +--com.gensym.util.DefinitionEvent
public class DefinitionEvent
extends EventObject
implements Serializable

An event that encapsulates a change made to a Classefinition in G2. It is spawned out of an ItemEvent from a Definition object.
